{"tid":1453420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒] 各位千祈唔好搞軍營","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:17:37.000Z","uid":26332,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee76e3db4d30f18596d87a5e8eee3b7b785a0944","tid":1453420,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:10:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747452&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=3cbe4ecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747452&h=3b90e5d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747452</a><br />\n據大陸消息人士透露，習總對處理香港亂局的最新指示是：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>無需動用部隊</ins></span>，用嚴刑峻法盡快平亂，寸土不讓。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有攬炒人士表示，雜種條垃圾越唔想出解放軍，就越要佢出，實行真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕對<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">唔建議</span></ins></strong>各位為攬炒，而去搞軍營！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d609cf1e5b9e394cd85def72018972769df6cf","tid":1453420,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67f42c5591ece782e794b9c1548ce842eee4afb","tid":1453420,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"c570d4facd131286a2e221b19ea7f87d12916779","tid":1453420,"uid":127528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08